    "description": "<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin: 0.5em 0px; color: #191813; font-family: Signika, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">Prerequisite: 15th level, Diabolist archetype</em></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin: 0.5em 0px; color: #191813; font-family: Signika, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\"><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\"><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\"><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">You are immune to necrotic damage, you are immune to disease, and you cannot be magically aged. When you kill a creature, you can either reduce your apparent age or extend your life span by a number of years equal to the creature&rsquo;s CR.</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">When you would die of old age, you instead become undead, gaining the skeleton or zombie template&nbsp;</span><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">with no changes to your ability scores.</span></span></span></span></p>",
